/#
   
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.GenericCommodityDeliveryPeriod {
  # Specifies the Applicable Day with respect to a range of Settlement Periods.
  applicableDay : FpML5.reporting.DayOfWeekExtEnum?

  # Specifies the hour-ending Start Time with respect to a range of Settlement Periods.
  startTime : FpML5.reporting.OffsetPrevailingTime?

  # Specifies the hour-ending End Time with respect to a range of Settlement Periods. If neither startTime nor endTime contain an offset element and endTime is earlier than startTime, this indicates that the time period "wraps around" midnight. For example, if startTime is 23:00 and endTime is 01:00 then Settlement Periods apply from 00:00 to 01:00 and 23:00 to 00:00 on each included day.
  endTime : FpML5.reporting.OffsetPrevailingTime?

}

applicableDay.Doc: Specifies the Applicable Day with respect to a range of Settlement Periods.
applicableDay.Name: applicableDay

startTime.Doc: Specifies the hour-ending Start Time with respect to a range of Settlement Periods.
startTime.Name: startTime

endTime.Doc: Specifies the hour-ending End Time with respect to a range of Settlement Periods. If neither startTime nor endTime contain an offset element and endTime is earlier than startTime, this indicates that the time period "wraps around" midnight. For example, if startTime is 23:00 and endTime is 01:00 then Settlement Periods apply from 00:00 to 01:00 and 23:00 to 00:00 on each included day.
endTime.Name: endTime
